Valkuil servers

To run, invoke the following:

in antalb@applejack:/scratch2/www/webservices-lst/live/repo/valkuil/valkuil-servers:

% timblserver --config=confusibles.conf &

% wopr -r server_sc -p ibasefile:ValkuilCorpus.1.1.tok.1Mlines.txt.l3r3_-a1+D.ibase,timbl:"-a1 +D",lexicon:ValkuilCorpus.1.1.tok.1Mlines.txt.lex,port:2001,keep:1,mwl:5,max_distr:250 &

timblserver runs on port 2000; wopr runs on port 2001.

(In Tilburg, the timbl spellmods initially ran on four machines; the WOPR servers ran on two machines. The timbl server would be run on bythos|chronos|sphinx|phoenix:/exp/antalb/valkuil/valkuil-servers, and the WOPR server would be run on bythos|phoenix:/exp/antalb/valkuil/valkuil-servers)

